(1) Rockaway Ave., east side, south from Ditmas Ave. In the foreground, is the Rockaway Ave., Trolley Line. The 2-story building below the mast, is No. 1095 Rockaway Ave.

July 30, 1935.

P. L. Sperr.

(2) The same a further view south, from 1095; at the right is Ditmas Ave. In the background is the trestle of the Long Island R.R. freight division.

July 30, 1935.

P. L. Sperr.
